{"type": "article", "id": 4327, "title": "Menu 啤酒发泡器", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-12T07:50:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233335JkMiYHq9KLRxnFWa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在品尝红酒前，好酒之人总会有许多技巧能让其风味更佳，那么啤酒呢？今年，来自丹麦的设计团队 Norm Architects 就为丹麦设计品牌 Menu 设计了一款名为「 Beer Foamer」的啤酒发泡器，可以让啤酒的泡沫更为绵密细致。Beer Foamer 的操作非常简单，只需在泡发瓶里倒入 1 厘米高度左右的啤酒，按下按钮，等待 20 秒，即可产出如拿铁奶泡一般的啤酒泡沫。定价 299.95 丹麦克朗（约合人民币 310 元），<a href=\"http://menu.as/shop/kitchen/tool/beer-foamer\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233332hJEKBulTvtLR3Y9F.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333334r7nFfUE9mjTQlhb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233334UXJu73jP6AbIBg2L.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"png\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}